imdb.plot outline: Gustav's Super Races shows you the worlds fastest cars put against each other in adrenaline-filled drag races. Gustav runs a successful YouTube channel with soon over 200 million views and a great reputation within the world of racing. The show presents the best races he's ever organized. With rare supercars from Bugatti, Koenigsegg, Ferrari an other top brands, these races share an unique look at the raw performance of the worlds fastest cars.
imdb.title: Gustav's Super Races
